    <item>
      <title>布达佩斯取消“迷你迪拜”土地交易 给奥尔班带来打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/budapest-torpedoes-mini-dubai-property-deal-in-blow-to-orban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利政府接受了首都的优先购买权，购买了布达佩斯市中心一块大片地块，而匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班原本想将其出售给一家阿布扎比的开发商，用于建造一个摩天大楼林立的社区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/budapest-torpedoes-mini-dubai-property-deal-in-blow-to-orban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:04:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
